          <p>Do you need to <strong>calculate the dimensions of your cross-=
stitch project</strong>? No problem! Use this <strong>cross stitch calculat=
or</strong> in order to know the measurement of your finished cross stitch =
project. You can also add some extra room for margins and framing, and be s=
ure you know&nbsp;<strong>what size fabric to use.</strong></p>

<h2>Cross Stitch Calculator</h2>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><label for=3D"patternWidth">Pattern width (number of stitches):</label>=
</td>
<td><input id=3D"patternWidth" type=3D"number"></td>
</tr>
